{"tid":1375563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下家母最近同藍絲朋友嘅對話","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:57:30.000Z","uid":22452,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"405671129d92c5f6ffd01abad91502553c06a5b3","tid":1375563,"uid":22452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"家母一直係淡黃，支持遊行但唔會自己出黎<br />\n發生左元朗單嘢之後，家母就覺得好氣憤<br />\n事緣今日家母同藍絲師奶飲茶，講起元朗單嘢<br />\n<br />\n藍絲師奶：班暴徒唔去搞啲警察點會俾人打呀，抵死啦，而家都係懲罰佢地<br />\n<br />\n家母：你睇清楚啦，你睇咩新聞呀，俾人剪輯曬，遊行就要俾人打，啲人無自由咩？<br />\n<br />\n藍絲師奶：唔係佢地出黎反政府，警察政府邊洗搵黑社會幫手？<br />\n<br />\n家母：班後生仔驚俾人拉左返大陸人間蒸發左呀！你試下諗下如果係你啲仔月俾人拉左返大陸你出唔出黎示威呀。<br />\n<br />\n藍絲師奶：我生係中國人，死係中國鬼。<br />\n<br />\n家母回應唔到佢句白痴對白，<br />\n於是教佢睇蘋果動新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家母頭先食飯對住我屌曬鬼話啲人唔用腦，好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家平日不妨教多啲屋企人用電話，<br />\n佢學識左用蘋果動之後好少睇tvb，<br />\n最近仲漸漸勇武左，<br />\n開始屌鳩啲屌人收錢嘅師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74b83f3b4c9c51ceeae2fbf4010daa1f85b4995","tid":1375563,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ef3f9301195e8660023425ce965c55bd72d4de2","tid":1375563,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"$3 藍變黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}